    "Management": {
      "text": "Use\nBenzodiazepines\nas first line agent for agitation, hypertension, and hyperthermia\nMay also use Nitroprusside or Phentolamine\nTreat with fluid resuscitation to avoid renal failure secondary to rhabdomyolysis (see below)",
      "subsections": {
        "Avoid": {
          "text": "Avoid\nsuccinylcholine\ndue to potential for\nhyperkalemia\nin these patients\nAvoid antipyretics\nAvoid pure\nbeta-blockers",
          "tables": []
        }
      },
